

[ Alt + y|u|b|n ]=move focused window rightup|leftup|rightdown|leftdown corners
[ Print ]=dmenu screenshot
[ Super + . ]=proces
[ Super + { ]=decrease gaps in tilling mode
[ Super + } ]=increase gap in tilling mode
[ Super + 1|2|2|4 ]=go to workspace 1|2|3|4
[ Super + a ]=xclock
[ Super + c ]=selection to clipboard
[ Super + e ]=expo grid mode
[ Super + F11 ]=fullscreen
[ Super + i ]=show/hide barpanel
[ Super + l|h|j|k ]=move focused window right|left|down|up
[ Super + m ]=single monocule layout
[ Super + Menu ]=fzf_prompt
[ Super + Minus ]=decrease master area in tilling mode
[ Super + n ]=focus next window
[ Super + p ]=focus prev window
[ Super + Pause ]=dmenu musicplayer
[ Super + Plus ]=increase master area in tilling mode
[ Super + q ]=kill window
[ Super + r ]=rename window
[ Super + space ]=terminal-togle
[ Super + t ]=tilling
[ Super + u ]=unmap terminal
[ Super + Return ]=launch xterm
[ Super + Shift + 1|2|3|4 ]=move focused window to workspace 1|2|3|4
[ Super + Shift + c ]=cat to clipboard
[ Super + Shift + e ]=nowm session manager
[ Super + Shift + h ]=decrease focused window -10 in horizontal
[ Super + Shift + j ]=increase focused window +10 in vertical
[ Super + Shift + k ]=decrease focused window -10 in vertical 
[ Super + Shift + l ]=increase focused window +10 in horizontal
[ Super + Shift + m ]=general monocule layout
[ Super + Shift + n ]=next workspace
[ Super + Shift + p ]=prev workspace
[ Super + Shift + u ]=map terminals
[ Super + Tab ]=cicle the opened terminals
[ Super + w ]=select window
[ XF86AudioLowerVolume ]=audio volume down
[ XF86AudioMute ]=pulsemixer
[ XF86AudioRaiseVolume ]=audio volume up
